    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292810/extras/132f4558c4c7c721d31a8c5b0d564591.webp?t=1651824642\" width=630 height=50 /></span><br>《山海旅人》是一款受传统中国神话启发的2D冒险解谜游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292810/extras/441b0a7f1edcad2a58c54439cd4471c2.poster.avif?t=1651824642\" width=622 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292810/extras/441b0a7f1edcad2a58c54439cd4471c2.webm?t=1651824642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292810/extras/441b0a7f1edcad2a58c54439cd4471c2.mp4?t=1651824642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏用像素表现水墨画的风格，带领着玩家们感受民间志怪故事里的风景和人物，例如黄泉、黑白无常、牛头马面、土地公等。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292810/extras/083db57f8d7ba0ecd52e57855db13bb2.webp?t=1651824642\" width=630 height=50 /></span><br>玩家扮演主角七云，一个能回溯到人们的记忆碎片当中的 “逆梦师”。他可以通过收集“感知”改变他人的“内心”，对过去人们的行为产生影响，以此改变历史。每一次对过去的改变，将对新的“现在”产生意想不到的结果。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292810/extras/2b5f4e9043c04eac3f77a5d1e4dbee75.poster.avif?t=1651824642\" width=630 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292810/extras/2b5f4e9043c04eac3f77a5d1e4dbee75.webm?t=1651824642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1292810/extras/2b5f4e9043c04eac3f77a5d1e4dbee75.mp4?t=1651824642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.a